app.use(rateLimit({ windowMs: 60_000, max: 100 }));
```

### 3. No authentication/authorization on `/users` (OWASP A01: Broken Access Control, A07: Auth Failures) — High (if data is real)
`/users` returns PII (names + emails) with no auth. Even as mock data, this pattern tends to survive into production.

